OL,3,CLabour to push for school mobile phone
OL,4,Cban
OL,6,FScottish Labour will use its debating
OL,7,Ftime in Holyrood on Wednesday to push
OL,8,Ffor a ban on mobile phones in schools.
OL,10,FConcerns have been raised about
OL,11,Fbehaviour and attainment in schools in
OL,12,Fthe years since the pandemic, with
OL,13,Fsome suggesting barring devices from
OL,14,Fclassrooms as a way of improving the
OL,15,Fsituation.
