OL,6,FLast year, the Scottish Government
OL,7,Fsaid a blanket national ban would not
OL,8,Fbe "appropriate or feasible", but
OL,9,FEducation Secretary Jenny Gilruth said
OL,10,Fshe would back headteachers who took
OL,11,Fsuch a decision.
OL,13,FSpeaking ahead of the debate on
OL,14,FWednesday afternoon, Labour education
OL,15,Fspokeswoman Pam Duncan-Glancy said:
OL,16,F"Classrooms should be safe places to
OL,17,Flearn, but under the SNP violence is
OL,18,Fon the rise, bullying is rife and
OL,19,Fattention spans are shortening.
