OL,6,F"Teachers are going above and beyond
OL,7,Fto support pupils, but they are being
OL,8,Flet down by a vacuum in leadership
OL,9,Ffrom the SNP.
OL,11,F"We owe it to the next generation to
OL,12,Fgive them the best possible education
OL,13,Fand it is a total dereliction of duty
OL,14,Ffor the SNP to pass the buck on so
OL,15,Fmany of the key issues facing our
OL,16,Fschools.
